Development information:
- IDE: Qt Creator 2.0.1
- Qt version: 4.7.1
- Platform: Linux

What works:

- Store connections
- Perform SQL queries.
- Rudimanetary SQL syntax highlighting (missing commands)
- Browse schemas
- Browse tables
- Browse and edit records (Qt native mode)


